        .grid
          .row
            .col-50
              .question
                .header
                  h4 What exactly is a hackathon?
                img(src="assets/images/faq/what_is_a_hackathon.png")
                .content A hackathon is an event in which software developers, designers and entrepreneurs come together and work on an idea for a few days. The event will be sponsored by companies, that means we have exciting prizes and planned key notes for you! There is also a career fair waiting for you to be checked out and of course free food and drinks.
            .col-50
              .question
                .header
                  h4 Do I have to be a programmer to attend?
                img(src="assets/images/faq/programmer_to_attend.png")
                .content NO! We're looking for a diverse group of people who want to work on an idea for a few days. You're a designer? Help create the user interface. You're a business rockstar? Help create a business or customer plan. You want to try coding for the first time? We will have introduction workshops that will give you a first glance about coding.

          .row
            .col-50
              .question
                .header
                  h4 How many people will the hackathon have?
                img(src="assets/images/faq/how_many_people.png")
